  <brief_title>Efficacy of Octreotide Acetate and Cabergoline in Patients With Acromegaly</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Single Arm, Proof of Concept Study to Investigate the Efficacy of an 8 Month Combination Therapy of Octreotide and Cabergoline in Acromegalic Patients Only Partially Responsive to Somatostatin Analog Monotherapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
