  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will investigate the efficacy of a combination treatment with octreotide acetate
      and cabergoline in acromegalic patients that are only partially responsive to a somatostatin
      analog monotherapy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
